sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant GitHub
    participant MongoDB
    User->>Browser: Click "Login with GitHub"
    Browser->>Frontend: Redirect to /auth/github
    Frontend->>Backend: GET /auth/github
    Backend->>GitHub: OAuth Authorization
    GitHub->>User: Authorize App
    User->>GitHub: Approve
    GitHub->>Backend: Access Token
    Backend->>Frontend: Redirect with JWT
    Frontend->>User: Show CreateProfile Form
    User->>Frontend: Submit Profile Data
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/profiles
    Backend->>GitHub: Fetch User/Repos
    Backend->>MongoDB: Save Profile
    MongoDB->>Backend: Profile Saved
    Backend->>Frontend: Profile Data & Share URL
    Frontend->>User: Redirect to /profile/:username